 the State of the Nation''\n|rowspan=4|Legislative Building, [[Manila]]\n|rowspan=4|[[3rd Congress of the Philippines|3rd Congress]]\n|1st\n|rowspan=4|English\n|\n|\n|-\n|18\n|{{start date|1955|01|24}}\n|''Address on the State of the Nation''\n|2nd\n|\n|\n|-\n|19\n|{{start date|1956|01|23}}\n|''Address on the State of the Nation''\n|3rd\n|\n|\n|-\n|20\n|{{start date|1957|01|28}}\n|''Address on the State of the Nation''\n|4th\n|\n|\n|-\n|21\n|rowspan=4 valign=top|[[File:Carlos P Garcia.jpg|100px]]<br>[[Carlos P. Garcia]]\n|{{start date|1958|01|27}}\n|''Address on the State of the Nation''\n|rowspan=4|Legislative Building, [[Manila]]\n|rowspan=4|[[4th Congress of the Philippines|4th Congress]]\n|1st\n|rowspan=4|English\n|\n|\n|-\n|22\n|{{start date|1959|01|26}}\n|''Address on the State of the Nation''\n|2nd\n|\n|\n|-\n|23\n|{{start date|1960|01|25}}\n|''Address on the State of the Nation''\n|3rd\n|\n|\n|-\n|24\n|{{start date|1961|01|23}}\n|''Address on the State of the Nation''\n|4th\n|\n|\n|-\n|25\n|rowspan=4 valign=top|[[File:Diosdado Macapagal USS Oklahoma City 1962 cropped.jpg|100px]]<br>[[Diosdado Macapagal]]\n|{{start date|1962|01|22}}\n|''Five-Year Integrated Socio-Economic Program for the Philippines''\n|rowspan=4|Legislative Building, [[Manila]]\n|rowspan=4|[[5th Congress of the Philippines|5th Congress]]\n|1st\n|rowspan=4|English\n|\n|\n|-\n|26\n|{{start date|1963|01|28}}\n|''The State of the Nation 1963''\n|2nd\n|\n|\n|-\n|27\n|{{start date|1964|01|27}}\n|''The State of the Nation''\n|3rd\n|\n|\n|-\n|28\n|{{start date|1965|01|25}}\n|''The Philippines after Three Years (1962\u20131965)''\n|4th\n|\n|\n|-\n|29\n|rowspan=20 valign=top|[[File:Ferdinand Marcos.JPEG|100px]]<br>[[Ferdinand Marcos]]\n|{{start date|1966|01|24}}\n|''Address on the State of the Nation''\n|rowspan=7|Legislative Building, [[Manila]]\n|rowspan=4|[[6th Congress of the Philippines|6th Congress]]\n|1st\n|rowspan=20|English\n|\n|\n|-\n|30\n|{{start date|1967|01|23}}\n|''The Epic of Nation-Bui